Homepage: Highlighting offers, new arrivals, and categories like skincare, makeup, etc.
Product Categories: Filters for price, brand, ratings, and more.
Product Details Page: Information, reviews, and add-to-cart functionality.
Cart and Checkout: A smooth shopping experience.
Search Bar: To quickly find products.
User Accounts: Login/signup, wishlist, and order history.
